### `/imagine:batch <prompt-file>` — Batch generate from a list

Reads a `.txt` or `.json` prompt file, one prompt per line/entry.

```
/imagine:batch ./prompts.txt --model flash --size 1024 --ar 16:9
```

Prompt file formats:
```txt
# prompts.txt — one per line
a red apple on a white table
a blue sports car on a mountain road
a neon-lit Tokyo street at night
```
```json
// prompts.json — with per-prompt overrides
[
  { "prompt": "a red apple", "ar": "1:1", "transparent": true },
  { "prompt": "Tokyo street at night", "ar": "16:9", "model": "pro" }
]
```

