## PROMPT ENGINEERING GUIDE

### Structure
```
[Subject] + [Action/Pose] + [Setting/Environment] + [Lighting] + [Style] + [Technical details]
```

### Quality Boosters
Append these to any prompt for better results:
- `highly detailed, sharp focus, 8K`
- `professional photography, studio lighting`
- `cinematic composition, golden hour`
- `photorealistic, hyperrealistic`
- `concept art, trending on ArtStation`
- `award-winning photography`

### Style Keywords
| Aesthetic | Keywords |
|-----------|----------|
| Photorealistic | `DSLR photo, f/1.8 aperture, bokeh, 50mm lens` |
| Cinematic | `anamorphic lens, film grain, color graded, widescreen` |
| Illustration | `digital illustration, clean linework, flat colors` |
| Pixel Art | `16-bit pixel art, NES palette, isometric, retro` |
| Anime | `anime style, studio ghibli, cel shading, vibrant` |
| Oil Painting | `oil on canvas, impasto, brushstrokes, renaissance` |
| Watercolor | `watercolor wash, soft edges, paper texture` |
| 3D Render | `Blender render, Octane renderer, subsurface scattering` |
| Minimalist | `minimal, white background, single subject, clean` |
| Dark Fantasy | `grimdark, dramatic shadows, atmospheric, moody` |

### Negative Prompts (`--negative`)
Common exclusions:
```
--negative "blurry, low quality, watermark, text, logo, bad anatomy, extra limbs, deformed"
--negative "NSFW, violence, realistic faces" (for illustrated styles)
--negative "overexposed, underexposed, noise, grain" (for photography)
```

