## CONFIGURATION

Set persistent defaults in `.nano-banana.json` (project root) or `~/.nano-banana.json` (global):

```json
{
  "defaultModel": "flash",
  "defaultSize": 1024,
  "defaultAspectRatio": "1:1",
  "defaultFormat": "png",
  "outputDir": "./generated",
  "costTracking": true,
  "apiKey": "${GEMINI_API_KEY}",
  "watermark": false,
  "maxBatchSize": 8
}
```

Environment variable: `GEMINI_API_KEY=your-key-here`

